# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# Types: feat, fix, refactor, docs, test, chore, ci, perf, style, build
# Scope: ingest, warehouse, entities, workflows, vectors, report, config
#
# Subject: imperative mood, no period at end, max 50 chars
#
# Body: explain WHAT and WHY, not HOW (wrap at 72 chars)
#
# Footer: BREAKING CHANGE:, Closes #issue, Refs #issue
#
# Examples:
#   feat(ingest): add workstream summary parser
#   fix(warehouse): handle null timestamps in events
#   refactor(config): move workspace into me_ops/
#   docs: update README with ingestion instructions
